# doctor.tape
Output docs/demo-doctor.gif

Require brain

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

Type `brain doctor "git push origin nonexistent-branch"`
Enter
Sleep 8s

Sleep 5s

# 选第一个选项 Run: git checkout -b nonexistent-branch（默认已选中）
Enter
Sleep 5s